properties.areaDesc: Northern Monterey Bay; San Francisco Peninsula Coast; Santa Cruz Mountains
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 29 at 12:39PM PST until March 2 at 9:00AM PST by NWS San Francisco CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...North winds 15 to 25 mph with gusts up to 35 mph
expected.

* WHERE...San Francisco Peninsula Coast, Santa Cruz Mountains
and Northern Monterey Bay.

* WHEN...From 4 PM Sunday to 9 AM PST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects.
Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may
result.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Fuels are at record dry levels for this
time of year. Use extreme caution with ignition sources and any
outdoor burning.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT FROM 4 PM SUNDAY TO 9 AM PST MONDAY
